data.text:
2023-24 Topps Museum Collection UEFA Champions League Checklist, Team Set Lists and Details

When you click on links to various merchants on this site, like eBay, and make a purchase, this can result in this site earning a commission.

Jump to the 2023-24 Topps Museum Collection UEFA Champions League checklist.

2023-24 Topps Museum Collection UEFA Champions League soccer cards get right to the big stuff with an autograph, relic and autographed relic in every single-pack hobby box. As with past years for the brand, the checklist includes a deep dive into the league’s players, particularly when it comes to autograph signers.

2023-24 Topps Museum Collection UEFA Champions League Checklist Overview

Archival Autographs represent the largest portion of Museum Collection’s ink. Over 100 different cards are available here alone, although many signers have multiple cards. Five different Archival Dual Autographs can also be found. Each of these pairs up two teammates.

For those looking for even more players, three different Supreme book cards (autograph, relic and autographed relic) each have 10 top-level standouts.

Framed Autographs are one of the defining features of the brand. This dates back to its debut more than a decade ago in baseball. In addition to the standard versions, there are Legendary Ink Framed Autographs, Framed Hat Trick autographed memorabilia cards that are exclusive to Hat Trick boxes, and Museum Framed Autograph Patch cards.

Another cornerstone is Momentous Material. These have jumbo relics with and without autographs.

Other signature themes include Kit Construction Triple Relic Autograph Books, Legacy Laces Autograph Relics, Marks of Excellence Autographs, Museum Autographed Relics, Rookie Reverence Autographs, Showpiece Signature Autograph Relics, and Single-Player Signature Swatches Dual Relic Autographs.

Among the memorabilia inserts are Single-Player Triple Relics, Rookie Reverence Relics, and Meaningful Material Single Relics.

The 2023-24 Topps Museum Collection UEFA checklist isn’t exclusively hits. A standard, albeit premium, base set is also part of the release. It consists of 100 cards and has a mix of current stars, past stars and rookies.

Five levels of parallels combine to land one per hobby box.

2023-24 Topps Museum Collection UEFA Champions League soccer cards at a glance:

Cards per pack: Hobby – 8

Packs per box: Hobby – 1

Boxes per case: Hobby – 12

Set size: 100 cards

Release date: June 28, 2024
